# Expo + RN Dev Guide

## General Specs  
Expo^TS^RN^func^decl^iter^mod^no-class^strict^a11y^dark^perf^nav^safe^err^i18n^sec^

### Code Style  
Style: TS-only, iface>type, no enum, desc-vars (isX), mod files: exp-comp → subcomp → helpers → static → types  
Naming: dash-dir, named exp only  
Syntax: `function`, decl JSX, concise cond (no braces for 1-liners), Prettier fmt  

### UI + Styling  
UI: Expo comp, Flexbox + useWindowDim, TW or styled-components, `useColorScheme`, high a11y (ARIA/native props), anim w/ reanimated+gesture-handler  

### Safe Area  
SafeArea: wrap w/ SafeAreaProvider+SafeAreaView, use SafeAreaScrollView, no hardcoded padding  

### Perf  
Perf: min useState/useEffect, prefer context+reducer, lazy load (Susp, dyn import), memo/useMemo/useCallback, opt images (WebP, lazy), splash/AppLoading, use Expo+RN dev tools  

### Navigation  
Nav: react-navigation (stack/tab/drawer), expo-router for dyn routes, deep/univ links  

### State  
State: useReducer+Context, react-query (cache, no spam calls), Zustand/RTK for complex, handle URLs via expo-linking  

### Errors  
Err: Zod validation, Sentry/expo-error-reporter, early return > nesting, no `else` after `if`, global boundaries  

### Testing  
Test: Jest+RNTL (unit), Detox (integration), Expo test tools, snapshot test if needed  

### Security  
Sec: sanitize input, use `react-native-encrypted-storage`, HTTPS+auth, Expo sec guide: expo.dev/guides/security  

### i18n  
i18n: `react-native-i18n` or `expo-localization`, RTL/lang switch, a11y text scaling  

## Expo Conventions  
- Use managed workflow  
- Mobile Web Vitals: Load, Jank, Resp  
- `expo-constants` = env  
- `expo-permissions` = dev perms  
- `expo-updates` = OTA  
- Docs: [expo.dev](https://docs.expo.dev), [distribution](https://docs.expo.dev/distribution/introduction/)
